features: 【The Productive Home Work Station Pro】Loomie L-shaped Desk is your key to optimizing your workspace. Its riser shelf effortlessly accommodates multiple monitors, laptops, printers, and other office essentials. The roomy desktop unleashes your creativity. What's more, the 4 open shelves on the side, complete with a convenient drawer and storage bag, keep everything you need within arm's reach. With built-in power outlets for quick charging of your smart devices, it's a productivity powerhouse.

【Adds New Ambiance with Smart RGB LED System】Take command with the smart app or the included IR remote. Choose from a staggering array of 60,000 colors and multiple dynamic modes. Easily match the RGB LED lighting to your home decor or tailor it to suit your study, work, or gaming ambiance. The lights even sync with your work, study, or gaming environment's rhythm, creating a serene workspace or an electrifying gaming setup that immerses you completely.

【Personalized & Ergonomic Design】Our thoughtfully designed monitor stand lets you position your screen at eye level, promoting good posture and reducing strain on your back and neck. The removable drawer and storage bag on the shelf provide ample space for organizing your various study and office supplies, as well as files.

【Chic Industrial Vintage Design】The rich wood grain finish is complemented by an industrial black metal frame, delivering a distinctive industrial aesthetic that's both simple and visually appealing. It's ideal as a home office desk, study writing table, or dedicated workspace. The rustic brown color exudes a retro and classic vibe, fitting seamlessly with any home decor style. The warm tones create a cozy atmosphere for your study or work.

【High-caliber Quality & Sturdy Construction】Crafted from durable commercial-grade laminate and a metal frame that can endure the rigors of daily use for years to come, this reversible L-shaped desk is a guarantee of quality. The full-frame metal construction and adjustable non-slip leg pads enhance stability. Overall, it's the perfect-sized reversible computer desk to enhance any home space.

【Easy to Assemble, Clear Instruction】​ All components and accessories are meticulously numbered, and the step-by-step instructions make assembly a breeze. Plus, if you encounter any issues with the product, don't hesitate to reach out to us. We're committed to resolving any problems within 24 hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I bought this desk for my 9th grader- which is home schooled. She loves it. I also bought the white marble desk for my 6th grade daughter. Both desks have the power choice upgrade. This desk is a strong and sturdy. Most of all looks great. Since I'm a widow mom, it was a little hard for me to put together- my kids helped me. But the instructions where step by step, with pictures. The box is very heavy to move around- but once the desk is put together it is very easy to move from spot to spot. Great desk for the value. If I ever need another desk, I would buy these again. Customer for life!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to assemble
reviews.reviewText: Desk is perfect for home office. Easy to assemble. Sturdy desk with lots of storage space. Great value for money. I like the wrap around monitor stand that leaves desktop clear for plenty of workspace.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Solid desk. Instructions could be better.
reviews.reviewText: Let’s start out with the positives:This desk is solid. It has metal framing and the wood is not the cheap particle board type wood that you might find on other build-it-yourself desks. It also did not take too long to build with me and one other person.The cons:I only really have two little negatives about this desk. First, the drawer is a fabric drawer so it’s pretty flimsy. And lastly, the directions are not great. It only really has pictures. I could figure it out but what they don’t really tell you is that you have to put a certain end in a certain spot. So I had to redo a couple of steps.No big deal though. I would buy this desk again. It has a lot of room and it’s the perfect size desk for what I wanted.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Son loves it
reviews.reviewText: We homeschool our son, he loves this desk. The size is perfect, the shelving and electrical on top is great. However, the lights that come with it.....they don't stay so wonderful. We went and crazy glued it. Putting it together was ok, but not great. Please read allllll directions before you even start, you will miss something. The price was ok. No real place to put your desk top to get it out of the way other then the floor. The draw that comes with is is made out of a fabric, my son doesn't use it that much. The side compartment is awesome. He puts his iPad that he needs for school in there.,

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This desk is well designed. It has metal press-fit nuts in all the parts which make it stronger and easier to assemble. Assembly was easy and only had one screw that would not accept the allen wrench. It is a nice looking desk also. The drawer is not the best, but overall and sturdy desk. I was impressed at how easy it was to put together. Just make sure to make sure all the parts are oriented as depicted in the instructions and pay attention to where the holes are at.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: This desk works perfect in my son’s room. He loves lights and that the power strip is built into the top of the desk. It includes 4 outlets and 2 usb connections. The desk seems sturdy. I wish it had a regular drawer, but the description even said it was a fabric drawer. It seems to work well with storing his x-box games and attachments though. The picture on the directions is opposite of what it appears. We ended up putting the shelf on the wrong side when we were putting the desk together, so we had to backtrack and fix the direction, which was annoying. Other than that, I feel like it will hold up for a long time. I feel like we got a great price for this desk considering the quality. My son is very happy with his new desk.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Easy to put together, sturdy, and tons of storage!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My daughter-in-law had to help me put it together and the instructional pictures were confusing to follow. But we did it. It's VERY heavy. But that makes it very sturdy. I bought the faux marble and love it.
